text: Mariia Miliaeva (born 16 July 2001) is a Russian road and track cyclist. She competed at the 2021 UCI Track Cycling World Championships, in the women's madison event. She rode for the COGEAS METTLER LOOK PRO CYCLING TEAM, and A.R. MONEX WOMEN'S PRO CYCLING TEAM. == References == == Other websites == * Mariia Miliaeva of Russia and A.R.
